"aoauth-debug/. Nginx ignores .htaccess, so block direct access to /wp-"
"content/uploads/aoauth-debug/ in the server block."
msgstr ""
"Apache et LiteSpeed utilisent la protection .htaccess générée dans uploads/"
"aoauth-debug/. Nginx ignore .htaccess, bloquez donc l’accès direct à /wp-"
"content/uploads/aoauth-debug/ dans le bloc serveur."

